ively.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Pro-QCP delivers a superior, inspection-ready Individualized Quality Control Plan that is CLSI, CLIA, CAP, TJC and ISO compliant.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Pro-QCP implements a continuous quality improvement (CQI) process, identifying additional process controls – specific for your lab – that can mitigate error. ‘CLIA\' to read: Streamlines CLIA and ISO 15189 compliance.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Pro-QCP has been demonstrated to save a typical lab thousands of hours of staff time</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:verdure/home-control-plan -->\n\n<!-- wp:verdure/section -->\n<section class=\"alignwide section\"><div class=\"section__inner\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"important-workflow-section\"} -->\n<p class=\"important-workflow-section\">In summary, Pro-QCP will optimize your most important workflow: delivering accurate test results</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></section>\n<!-- /wp:verdure/section -->\n\n<!-- wp:verdure/home-zero-risk-offer {\"className\":\"home-first-qcp-section\"} -->\n<div class=\"home-zero-risk-offer\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"home-zero-risk-offer-inner-blocks-container\"><!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Zero Risk Offer</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We want to demonstrate Pro-QCP\'s value to you, your lab, your healthcare org -- and your patients.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>For a limited time, CarePoint will provide your first Pro-QCP subscription at NO-CHARGE… a $3995 value.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Why so generous??? We believe that once you see Pro-QCP’s expansive content and comprehensive process, once you gain access to the actionable information that Pro-QCP can deliver, you’ll be compelled to purchase modules specific to each of your POCT platforms.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Check out this 5-minute video to get a peek under the hood… or better yet, access your FREE annual subscription right now and put Pro-QCP right to work for your patients.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\"><!-- wp:button -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"#\">5 Min PRO-QCP Tour</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button -->\n\n<!-- wp:button -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"#\">Free PRO-QCP Subscription 2</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":244,\"width\":\"550px\",\"height\":\"auto\",\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://carepoint-web.ddev.site/app/uploads/2024/09/bg5-361x432.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-244\" style=\"width:550px;height:auto\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:verdure/home-zero-risk-offer -->\n\n<!-- wp:verdure/image-section -->\n<div class=\"image-section\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"image-section-inner-blocks-container\"><!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Aenean commodo ligula eget dolor. Aenean massa.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":268,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure clas