rd-items\"><span class=\"img-box\"> <img src=\"https://carepoint-web.ddev.site/app/uploads/2024/09/11306291-1.svg\" alt=\"Icon\" style=\"width:24px;height:24px\"/> </span><h2>Easily demonstrate compliance</h2><p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.</p></li><li class=\"card-items\"><span class=\"img-box\"> <img src=\"https://carepoint-web.ddev.site/app/uploads/2024/09/1644330.svg\" alt=\"Icon\" style=\"width:24px;height:24px\"/> </span><h2>Harmonize lab processes</h2><p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.</p></li><li class=\"card-items\"><span class=\"img-box\"> <img src=\"https://carepoint-web.ddev.site/app/uploads/2024/09/9402263.svg\" alt=\"Icon\" style=\"width:24px;height:24px\"/> </span><h2>Identify areas for improvement</h2><p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.</p></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:verdure/home-cards --></div></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:verdure/home-iso-compliance -->\n\n<!-- wp:verdure/home-did-you-know {\"className\":\"home-qc-solutions\"} -->\n<div class=\"home-did-you-know\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"home-did-you-know-inner-blocks-container\"><!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":425,\"scale\":\"cover\",\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://carepoint-web.ddev.site/app/uploads/2024/09/Group-181.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-425\" style=\"object-fit:cover\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Did You Know?</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Medical errors claim the lives of over a quarter million people in the US each year.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Medical error is the third leading cause of fatalities in the US, just behind heart disease and cancer.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Each of us will likely experience a meaningful diagnostic error in our lifetime.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Diagnostic errors are increasing as the delivery of health care increases in complexity.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>5% of U.S. adults who seek outpatient care each year experience a diagnostic error.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Diagnostic errors contribute to approximately 10% of preventable patient deaths.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Diagnostic errors account for up to 17% of hospital adverse events.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Diagnostic errors are the leading type of paid medical malpractice claims.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>The average US hospital pays out more than $300 million each year in malpractice settlements.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Among medical errors, diagnostic errors are almost twice as likely to result in patient death..</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:verdure/home-did-you-know -->\n\n<!-- wp:verdure/vdslider {\"hasNavigation\":true,\"hasPagination\":true,\"hasLoop\":true,\"className\":\"vdslider\\u002d\\u002dhornetbox\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-verdure-vdslider vdslider vdslider--has-navigation vdslider--has-pagination vdslider--has-loop vdslider--hornetbox\" data-spacebetween=\"20\" data-maxitems=\"3.5\"><div class=\"swiper\"><div class=\"vdslider__items swiper-wrapper\"><!-- wp:verdure/vdslider-item -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-verdure-vdslider-item swiper-item swiper-slide\"><!-- wp:verdure/box -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-verdure-box box\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Slide 1</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:verdure/box --></div>\n<!-- /wp:verdure/vdslider-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:verdure/vdslider-item -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-verdure-vdslider-item swiper-item swiper-slide\"><!-- wp:verdure/box -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-verdure-box box\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Slide 2</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:verdure/box --></div>\n<!-- /wp:verdure/vdslider-item --></div><div class=\"swiper-pagination\"></div></div><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Previous slide\" class=\"vdslider__nav vdslider__nav--prev\"><svg class=\"icon\"><use href=\"/ico.svg#chevron-left\"></use></svg></button><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Next slide\" class=\"vdslider__nav vdslider__nav--next\"><svg class=\"icon\"><use href=\"/ico.svg#chevron-right\"></use></svg></button></div>\n<!-- /wp:verdure/vdslider -->', 'Homepage', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '313-revision-v1', '', '', '2024-09-23 09:26:38', '2024-09-23 09:26:38', '', 313, 'https://carepoint-web.ddev.site/?p=432', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
