(541, 1, '2024-09-25 07:18:20', '2024-09-25 07:18:20', '<!-- wp:verdure/about-banner {\"imageUrl\":\"https://carepoint-web.ddev.site/app/uploads/2024/09/Mask-group.png\",\"imageId\":492} -->\n<div class=\"about-banner\"><div><img class=\"hero-img\" src=\"https://carepoint-web.ddev.site/app/uploads/2024/09/Mask-group.png\" alt=\"Selected image\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></div><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"inner-blocks-container\"><!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About CarePoint Solutions, Inc.</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:verdure/about-banner -->\n\n<!-- wp:verdure/about-first-section {\"className\":\"home-qa-software\"} -->\n<div class=\"about-first-section\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"about-first-section-inner-blocks-container\"><!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Founded in 2012,&nbsp; CarePoint Solutions&nbsp; designs, develops and commercializes products that improve the accuracy and reliability of diagnostic testing.</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With medical errors now the number #3 cause of fatalities in the US, and with diagnostic error associated with a majority of those errors, healthcare providers&nbsp;have a moral, ethical, legal, and financial responsibility to improve testing processes to ensure quality outcomes. CarePoint Solutions is dedicated to&nbsp;delivering the tools and resources needed by healthcare providers to accomplish this goal.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>CarePoint’s QA&nbsp;Software Division&nbsp;is focused on leveraging information technology and develop